---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Hummingbird Social Studio | Wedding Invitation Templates & Editable Wedding Suites"
  description="Editable wedding invitation templates, wedding invitation suites, bridal shower invites, and printable wedding stationery with a warm mid-century modern style."
>
  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <p class="eyebrow">Editable wedding templates</p>
        <h1>Beautiful wedding stationery made simple.</h1>
        <p class="lead">Hummingbird Social Studio creates editable wedding invitation suites, bridal shower invitations, menu cards, thank you cards, and printable wedding templates for modern celebrations.</p>
        <div class="button-row">
          <a class="button" href="/wedding-invitation-suites/">Browse Invitation Suites</a>
          <a class="button secondary" href="/bridal-shower-invitations/">Explore Bridal Shower Invites</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">Shop by category</p>
        <h2>Wedding templates for every little detail.</h2>
        <div class="grid">
          <a class="card" href="/wedding-invitation-suites/"><h3>Wedding Invitation Suites</h3><p>Editable invitation sets with matching RSVP cards, detail cards, and coordinated wedding stationery.</p></a>
          <a class="card" href="/bridal-shower-invitations/"><h3>Bridal Shower Invitations</h3><p>Pretty, easy-to-edit bridal shower invite templates for brunches, garden parties, and modern celebrations.</p></a>
          <a class="card" href="/contact/"><h3>Custom Requests</h3><p>Need a matching menu, thank you card, or wedding sign? Reach out for template questions and custom ideas.</p></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="feature-band">
      <div class="container content">
        <p class="eyebrow">Why digital templates?</p>
        <h2>Download, edit, print, and celebrate.</h2>
        <p>Our templates are designed for couples who want polished wedding stationery without starting from scratch. Edit the wording, update your details, download your files, and print at home or through your favorite print shop.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
